  74,38,"kl nafs bima kasabat min 'aemal alsharu walsuw' mhbwst mrhwnt bksbha, la tufakk hataa tuadiy ma ealayha min alhuquq waleqwbat, 'iilaa almuslimin almukhlasin 'ashab alyamin aladhin fkku rqabhm baltaet, hum fi janaat la yudrak wsfha, yas'al baeduhum bedana ean alkafirin aladhin 'ajramuu fi haqi anfshm: ma aldhy adkhlkm jhnm, wajaealakum tdhwqwn seyrha? qal almjrmwn: lam nakun min almsllin fi aldnya, walam nakun ntsdq wnhsn lilfuqara' walmsakyn, wakunaa natahadath bialbatil mae 'ahl alghawayt waldlalt, wakunaa nukadhib biawm alhisab waljza', hataa ja'ana almwt, wanahn fi tilk aldlalat walmnkrat"
